{"title":"HTML 文件的跳脫字元","uid":"3cd6dfa1f1d694a9161229865a57df9f","slug":"html-escape-character","date":"2022-08-19T13:36:00.000Z","updated":"2022-12-25T14:20:23.070Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/html-escape-character.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>在你編寫 HTML 文件時，你經常所使用的 <code>&lt;</code> 和 <code>&gt;</code> 字符，想必對你並不陌生。</p>\n<p>可是，你有沒有想過，HTML 看重的以上那些字符，若要把它們實際顯示出來，應要怎麼辦呢？</p>\n<p>原來，在電腦科學，有一個概念叫做<strong>跳脫字元</strong>（escape character）。</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"跳脫。。字元？！\"><a href=\"#跳脫。。字元？！\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"跳脫。。字元？！\"></a>跳脫。。字元？！</h1><p>哈哈！聽起來它很像如其名一樣活潑呢！其實並不是這樣，所謂的跳脫字元，其實是什麼呢？</p>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">參考資料：<a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-tw/biztalk/core/escape-characters\" target=\"_blank\">Microsoft</a></p>\n<p>逸出字元是單一字元，用來抑制跟隨在它後面之字元的任何特殊意義。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">TIP</p>\n<p>跳脫字元又稱轉義字元或逸出字元。</p>\n</div>\n<p>簡而言之，就是把程序碼上的字符<strong>無效化</strong>，並把其當作普通字符顯示。</p>\n<p>例如，就以定義段落 <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> 為例，這個標示原本就會把新的段落定義於 HTML 文件裏，如果我們想運用跳脫字元呢？</p>\n<p>要顯示完整的 <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> 整個字串，就需要使用 HTML 的跳脫字元。</p>\n<hr>\n<h1 id=\"HTML-的跳脫字元\"><a href=\"#HTML-的跳脫字元\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"HTML 的跳脫字元\"></a>HTML 的跳脫字元</h1><div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">跳脫字元</p>\n<p>顯示 <code>&lt;</code> : 使用 <code>&amp;lt;</code><br>顯示 <code>&gt;</code> : 使用 <code>&amp;gt;</code></p>\n</div>\n<p>因此，若要顯示 <code>&lt;p&gt;</code>，就需要鍵入：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">&amp;lt;p&amp;gt;</code></pre>\n\n<p>看到這裏，或許你會有一個疑問，就是為什麼我可以把這些跳脫字元顯示出來呢，因為理論上它們會被轉義為相應字元欸。</p>\n<p>的確，但原來在 HTML，<code>&amp;</code> 也被認定，所以，若要顯示 <code>&amp;</code>，就需要鍵入：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">&amp;amp;</code></pre>\n\n<p>大概就是這樣了，HTML 提供許多跳脫字元，在這裏無法一一羅列，可到 <a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/named-characters.html#named-character-references\" target=\"_blank\">完整總表</a> 看看，下面有一個簡潔的常用跳脫字元總表，大家可以用作參考：</p>\n<table>\n    <tr>\n        <th width=\"20%\">顯示</th>\n        <th>跳脫字元</th>\n        <th>備註</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>&nbsp;</td>\n        <td>&amp;nbsp;</td>\n        <td>no-break space（空格）</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>&lt;</td>\n        <td>&amp;lt;</td>\n        <td>less than</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>&gt;</td>\n        <td>&amp;gt;</td>\n        <td>greater than</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>&amp;</td>\n        <td>&amp;amp;</td>\n        <td>ampersand</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>&quot;</td>\n        <td>&amp:quot;</td>\n        <td>double quotation mark</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>&apos;</td>\n        <td>&amp;apos;</td>\n        <td>single quotation mark (apostrophe)</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>&cent;</td>\n        <td>&amp;cent;</td>\n        <td>cent</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>&pound;</td>\n        <td>&amp;pound;</td>\n        <td>pound</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>&yen;</td>\n        <td>&amp;yen;</td>\n        <td>yen</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>&euro;</td>\n        <td>&amp;euro;</td>\n        <td>euro</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>&copy;</td>\n        <td>&amp;copy;</td>\n        <td>copyright</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td>&reg;</td>\n        <td>&amp;reg;</td>\n        <td>registered trademark</td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n\n<p>但是，若是經常要自己手動轉義，未免過於哀了吧。不用擔心，你可以用網上的資源，例如 <a href=\"https://www.techyleaf.in/p/free-html-parse-tool.html\" target=\"_blank\">線上 HTML 解析編輯器</a> ，它的作用就是把跳脫字元一律顯示出來。。</p>\n<hr>\n<p>就是這樣，希望大家瞭解到跳脫字元的基本運作，再見。</p>\n","text":"在你編寫 HTML 文件時，你經常所使用的 &lt; 和 &gt; 字符，想必對你並不陌生。 可是，你有沒有想過，HTML 看重的以上那些字符，若要把它們實際顯示出來，應要怎麼辦呢？ 原來，在電腦科學，有一個概念叫做跳脫字元（escape character）。 跳脫。。字元？！...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.6k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"網頁開發","slug":"網頁開發","count":7,"path":"api/categories/網頁開發.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"HTML","slug":"HTML","count":3,"path":"api/tags/HTML.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%B7%B3%E8%84%AB%E3%80%82%E3%80%82%E5%AD%97%E5%85%83%EF%BC%9F%EF%BC%81\"><span class=\"toc-text\">跳脫。。字元？！</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#HTML-%E7%9A%84%E8%B7%B3%E8%84%AB%E5%AD%97%E5%85%83\"><span class=\"toc-text\">HTML 的跳脫字元</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"BlueWhaleYT","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://i.ibb.co/zRvn96K/20210718-233824.jpg","link":"/","description":"Everything is possible, as long as you are powerful.","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"動態載入 CSS 或 JavaScript 文件","uid":"39e2fe52ccd79c436e0898cd9cdd61f2","slug":"dynamic-load-css-and-js-file","date":"2022-09-09T09:38:52.000Z","updated":"2022-12-24T02:44:57.416Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/dynamic-load-css-and-js-file.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"去年，我撰寫了一篇文章，介紹過 Eruda 網頁源始碼線上檢查器，教導大家直接透過瀏覽器書籤直以呼喚這個程式，當然，它也還有其他方式呼喚的，不過這裏不作講解了，因為這個並不是這篇文章的重點。重點是 Eruda 檢查器是透過使用動態載入的方式把 JavaScript 文件載入至網站...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.8k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"網頁開發","slug":"網頁開發","count":7,"path":"api/categories/網頁開發.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":4,"path":"api/tags/CSS.json"},{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":4,"path":"api/tags/JavaScript.json"}],"author":{"name":"BlueWhaleYT","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://i.ibb.co/zRvn96K/20210718-233824.jpg","link":"/","description":"Everything is possible, as long as you are powerful.","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{"title":"解決固定導覽列與錨點的衝突","uid":"a4bc86905e91284a7270b344b882f194","slug":"solve-conflicts-with-navbar-and-anchor","date":"2022-08-15T13:46:00.000Z","updated":"2022-12-25T13:29:43.690Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/solve-conflicts-with-navbar-and-anchor.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"在我正在愁思應